#: ../../source/index.rst:10
msgid "Welcome to LMCache!"
msgstr "欢迎使用 LMCache！"

#: ../../source/index.rst:12
msgid "LMCache"
msgstr "LMCache"

#: ../../source/index.rst:20
msgid "**Supercharge Your LLM with the Fastest KV Cache Layer.**"
msgstr "**极速 KV Cache 层，让大模型告别重复计算，全面提升推理效率。**"

#: ../../source/index.rst:23
msgid ""
"We are currently in the process of upgrading our documentation to provide "
"better guidance and examples. Some sections may be under construction. Thank "
"you for your patience!"
msgstr ""
"我们目前正在升级文档，以提供更好的指导和示例。某些章节可能仍在建设中，感谢您"
"的耐心等待！"

#: ../../source/index.rst:36
msgid ""
"LMCache lets LLMs prefill each text only once. By storing the KV caches of "
"all reusable texts, LMCache can reuse the KV caches of any reused text (not "
"necessarily prefix) in any serving engine instance. It thus reduces prefill "
"delay, i.e., time to first token (TTFT), as well as saves the precious GPU "
"cycles and memory."
msgstr ""
"LMCache 让 LLM 对每段文本只需预填充一次。通过存储所有可复用文本的 KV 缓存，"
"LMCache 能在任意推理引擎实例中复用任意可复用文本（不必是前缀）的 KV 缓存。由此"
"既降低了预填充延迟（即首 token 时间，TTFT），又节省了宝贵的 GPU 算力与显存。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:38
msgid ""
"By combining LMCache with vLLM, LMCache achieves 3-10x delay savings and GPU "
"cycle reduction in many LLM use cases, including multi-round QA and RAG."
msgstr ""
"将 LMCache 与 vLLM 结合后，在多轮问答、RAG 等众多 LLM 应用场景中，LMCache 可实现"
" 3-10 倍的延迟节省并降低 GPU 算力消耗。"

